{
  "stem": "443.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know if you heard about this camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were a women department.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were women was separate than men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By the way, while-- while I'm talking about when we arrived to the train, there was another transport leaving Bergen-Belsen going to the train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we used the same train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But these people were kept in a separate area where they fed these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They looked good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were clothed in civil clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were older people, younger people, babies, children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was one part in Bergen-Belsen kept in good condition to show for the Red Cross that people are not being abused, that people are being well taken care of.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And at this transport, we found out later on, that the Satmar [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Eruv ?], the Great Chief Rebbe of Satmar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm sure, today, everybody knows who he was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was in that transport, surviving in Bergen-Belsen, being transported away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Where they went from there, we never know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it's funny how you think back to see that there were some people kept in good condition.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This is how they contrived-- they-- they-- they they tricked the world, that people didn't know what was really going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "While we were in Bergen-Belsen, we didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was no work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they just kept us there with no food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Maybe somebody will bring a bowl of soup, a little water, something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "For a few days, there was no food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Then they started to bring in some [? gamesa ?] soup, it's called.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It's made out of grass and bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that's what they cooked up for us, soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they gave us-- but it was good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was like you say, you could-- today, you eat filet mignon.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
